<a href="/questions/1648538-why-is-it-called-the-moon-and-sixpence">Why is it called the Moon and Sixpence?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1648538'><a id="like_count_community_question_1648538" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1648538?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F44796.The_Moon_and_Sixpence">like</a></span>

